1st. add buiscuit andmilk together until all the lumps are destroyed
2nd. before adding eno remember to keep the container ready(
    take a containe that can be used in microwave
    greese it(apply oil/butter in the container)or apply butter paper
    heat it for 30 sec 
)
now add eno and add a little milk so that a bubbles will appear so just stir it once or twice and just keep it cor baking in the microwave for 10 min